email_subject: change in date/time for Compaq's Experience ENRON
email_body: Carrie, I hope you had a great Thanksgiving! We would like to change the date for the Compaq Experience ENRON request I submitted online. Originally the date was 12/13, we would like to reschedule for 12/14 for one hour in the afternoon. Jennifer Stewart Medcalf will give you a call with further details. Colleen Koenig Analyst Enron Corp Global Strategic Sourcing 713.345.5326
